:Class DPB
    ⍝ Definite Progress Bar in Dyalog APL.
    
    :Field Private total ← ⍬
    :Field Private progress ← ⍬
    :Field Private defaults ← 100    ⍝ default set of options.
    
    ∇ InitDefault
        :Access Public
        :Implements Constructor
        Init defaults
    ∇
    
    ∇ Init length
        :Access Public
        :Implements Constructor
        
        total ← length
        progress ← 0        
    ∇
    
    ∇ dpb ← Start
    
    ∇
:EndClass



